cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "MycorrhizaTracer"
abstract: "A Python pipeline for processing Sanger sequencing data (ab1 files), generating consensus sequences, classifying them taxonomically using BLASTN against reference databases, clustering sequences into OTUs, and optionally salvaging low-quality reads. Designed for fungal (ITS) and plant (ITS2, RBCL) genes with functional annotation via FUNGuild."
authors:
